{
  "manifest_version": 1,
  "id": "themes_core",
  "name": "Core themes",
  "version": "0.9.0",
  "kind": "theme",
  "description": "46 hand-curated themes: a clean white 'Paper' default, 6 bold-accent white-bg themes (Cobalt, Flame, Magenta, Kelly, Royal, Cherry), 4 vibrant-fg themes that render typography in saturated ink rather than neutral grey (Ink: navy on cream; Burgundy: wine on parchment; Embers: orange on deep brown; Cyber: electric green on near-black), plus 15 monochromatic (5 light/mid/dark each), 15 duotone with complementary fg/bg hues, and 5 neon themes (Hotwire/Plasma/Matrix/Synthwave/Toxic) with vivid pink/purple/green accents on near-black bgs. The midtone palette deliberately uses tinted-paper bgs around L=0.70 so Spectra 6 dithers actual coloured ink rather than collapsing to white.",
  "supports": {
    "sizes": [
      "xs",
      "sm",
      "md",
      "lg"
    ]
  },
